0Z","msg":"國際標準=支那標準"},{"pid":"682625054f09cacd7591c8448b6a2bd824a48f23","tid":519262,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5e85cc0789b5d73ab83050a689f35520fdc70a09","tid":519262,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bb1dbea81a792365b48369d758f1bbc9dcbcee2","tid":519262,"uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"8ecde71fc8d26748201c1662dd8abf7cb4ced496","tid":519262,"uid":33848,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T07:48:03.000Z","msg":"不嬲都食泰國米"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:21:00.000Z","msg":"酒樓腸粉，粥，炒粉麵⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n仲有米線等等⋯<br />\n<br />\n實避唔哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:22:12.000Z","msg":"茶餐聽係咪用晒支那米？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:24:26.000Z","msg":"一定有平用平，好可能係"},{"pid":"ac683fa1ba3b75e8e14d079d06c14bc2e6ebfa50","tid":519262,"uid":126283,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:25:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>仲唔快啲感謝黨？<br />\n恩賜你地肉體上成為支那人</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"18fec0144fbc11e985d5929ff50dab95aba3bacd","tid":519262,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac683fa1ba3b75e8e14d079d06c14bc2e6ebfa50","tid":519262,"uid":126283,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:25:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>仲唔快啲感謝黨？<br />\n恩賜你地肉體上成為支那人</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:27:08.000Z","msg":"感謝黨賜給香港人元素表<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597385a7bf736307cbeaf2f141562cf556ceee72","tid":519262,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:33:42.000Z","msg":"食開金鳳唔會轉 轉都係轉日本米"},{"pid":"2ae256e51fe51273b9aeb858be7d0a832414fcfb",