2,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c37b6757963f794703aa41754bd0e89a418b409a","tid":519262,"uid":33357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6de113c13011c9fc64f3db370a1fd26c1c1fce51","tid":519262,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:44:34.000Z","msg":"已經戒左中國米製品好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T09:48:17.000Z","msg":"你唔會出街食?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T10:33:19.000Z","msg":"食開福喜雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f92f482795f930afb6dafbf5aeba6e044e852e","tid":519262,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T10:38:44.000Z","msg":"究竟奶共可以奶到咩地步"},{"pid":"ad54385913667347f91d56ff3e4d1f36445c520e","tid":519262,"uid":7067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T10:43:19.000Z","msg":"我真係唔明點解食物安全呢d標準會放寬而唔係收緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42fa7ef78d9769d827d4cef53819630d4868794","tid":519262,"uid":41693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T10:49:51.000Z","msg":"點解要放寬？ 為左更多供應？ <br />\n有無官方原因聽下？"},{"pid":"46872c6675d416282d038dd28ac5d2d2b21ec272","tid":519262,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:20:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要放寬？ 為左更多供應？ <br />\n有無官方原因聽下？</blockquote><br />\n香港人食中國米<br />\n中國人食外國米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係人都知係中國 做果樣就唔敢掂果樣養雞的人唔會食自己養的雞<br />\n種菜的人唔會食自己種的菜"},{"pid":"3d1a3d6860f637fc18e7a9cdcb5b9ca3a0fe0c9e","tid":519262,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:16:57.000Z","msg":"移民啦仲問"},{"pid":"d0271c610431080efe3e071d7c0425a9ad1fdfca","tid":519262,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:43:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">吉野家稱用「黑龍江日式米」　<br />\n網民憤怒了：中國米你食埋我個份 (13:25)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20151013/s00001/1444712962583SL4_7E4F4B97567A3CFC93566A1E0301B322.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20151013%2Fs00001%2F1444712962583SL4_7E4F4B97567A3CFC93566A1E0301B322.jpg&h=85500262&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港吉野家「我們憤怒了」的聲明傳遍Facebook，稱近日又收到誤傳他們用日本福島米飯的信息，忍無可忍報警處理，還作出安全承諾，指該店採用的是黑龍江日式珍珠米，不料卻釀成「公關災難」。<br />\n<br />\n吉野家在Facebook專頁稱，他們採用黑龍江黑土壤種植的日式珍珠米，而穀飼牛則主要來自美國優質認可農場，以上等粟米及小麥餵飼。<br />\n<br />\n不料，這個溫馨的「安全承諾」卻引來網民激烈反應。截至今午約1時，專頁已有逾千條留言批評吉野家標榜自己是日本食店，卻使用內地食材。有人說：「一直以為你哋用日本米先幫襯，你咁講一講，很有被欺騙嘅感覺」。更多網民說「你話用福島米我都冇咁驚」、「我寧願食福島米」、「中國米你食埋我個份」、「套餐成40蚊，仲要食大陸米，真係幫襯茶記好過」。"},{"pid":"30d4ba2427f68478a217c9c7165bb727e4c6bf49","tid":519262,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T13:59:33.000Z","msg":"癱仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78565e33cb6e9b3f3d0af39357b66450041ed875","tid":519262,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T01:04:56.000Z","msg":"性命悠關，大家留意下"},{"pid":"31803376ca42c40eb565fe4659fdced2e4f820b4","tid":519262,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T01:12:46.000Z","msg":"點放都唔撚柒會食中國米啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da31ed32f4a5602722747c9ae3df16bf5b174d67","tid":519262,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8f38682088f21fc50a9ad38c758af9003059345","tid":519262,"uid":63909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2ae256e51fe51273b9aeb858be7d0a832414fcfb","tid":519262,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"682625054f09cacd7591c8448b6a2bd824a48f23","tid":519262,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:24:26.000Z","msg":"一定有平用平，好可能係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:38:18.000Z","msg":"「喂，我最近有批好平既米，有需要就打呢個電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:39:48.000Z","msg":"鮑魚唔見你益我"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T01:13:08.000Z","msg":"咪撚柒戇鳩啦...以為中國米一定最平"},{"pid":"d2712790f59b45d4be103196b7685f486159a3db","tid":519262,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bec24c69e732ed9050e6b92762d5aca8d08d42ff","tid":519262,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f7a1e26bbc35f202155cc31c2ba5cade02fb028","tid":519262,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:18:09.000Z","msg":"倡放寬白米鎘含量受質疑 政府反駁引入劣質米說法「不科學」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180104/large/1515048207_8e1e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180104%2Flarge%2F1515048207_8e1e.png&h=78b6b82c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府準備向立法會提出《食物攙雜（金屬雜質含量）規例》修訂，建議<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">收緊多種食物的重金屬含量規管，但白米鎘含量上限由目前每公斤0.1毫克，放寬至0.2毫克。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>食物安全中心指有關建議獲米商支持，但在公眾諮詢時就收到個別意見反對。中心反駁過去數年抽驗逾400個白米樣本，只有1個樣本超出0.2毫克的新標準，認為放寬標準會引入劣質米的說法並不科學。<br />\n<br />\n本港食物過往是根據「固體」及「液體」分開作出規管，政府提出的新修訂就建議將食物細分成菜、海產、米等各類食物，並加強<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">將食物鉛含量將由每公斤6毫克，收緊至每公斤0.1至0.3毫克不等，並同時增加檢驗錳、鎳、銅、鈾等7種重金屬。</span></strong>食安中心解釋，現有法例已嚴重過時，今次修例是為與國際接軌，即使日後檢查不合格率可能輕微上升，但相信都不會影響各類食物的入口或供應，新法例亦會設有一至兩年適應期。<br />\n<br />\n至於海產，新例會要求龍蝦等甲殼類動物需要符合每公斤上限2毫克鎘的標準。食安中心同樣認為不會易響整體海產供應，惟當中對麵包蟹、斑馬瀨尿蝦、琵琶蝦、劍魚柳等鎘含量本身較高的食物，可能會因為規例收緊而增加不合格率，但中心認為這些食物一向供應較少，對整體影響不會大。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:22:44.000Z","msg":"國際標準=支那標準"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T01:13:27.000Z","msg":"樣樣收緊, 淨放鎘<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fb77ef4ad2bb080c19fec313cf11615910d946c","tid":519262,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31803376ca42c40eb565fe4659fdced2e4f820b4","tid":519262,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T01:12:46.000Z","msg":"點放都唔撚柒會食中國米啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T01:14:16.000Z","msg":"你唔出街食飯既？（又問多次）"},{"pid":"4282ae9a42740d94d0674e00f9f2d918299b068e","tid":519262,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da31ed32f4a5602722747c9ae3df16bf5b174d67","tid":519262,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8f38682088f21fc50a9ad38c758af9003059345","tid":519262,"uid":63909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2ae256e51fe51273b9aeb858be7d0a832414fcfb","tid":519262,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:38:18.000Z","msg":"「喂，我最近有批好平既米，有需要就打呢個電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:39:48.000Z","msg":"鮑魚唔見你益我"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T01:13:08.000Z","msg":"咪撚柒戇鳩啦...以為中國米一定最平"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T01:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d045fc18caaee417720af4d81f7374363f7a2fcc","tid":519262,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T01:28:57.000Z","msg":"食物安全只會隨年代越來越嚴謹"},{"pid":"5f54e04a03bc3f5d952a26211ff1b314427b56cb","tid":519262,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T01:34:27.000Z","msg":"